text: Frontenay-Rohan-Rohan is a commune in the Deux-Sèvres department in the Nouvelle-Aquitaine region in western France. It is located 10 km south of Niort on the route to La Rochelle. 3,000 inhabitants live there. ==See also== *Communes of the Deux-Sèvres department ==References== *INSEE Category:Communes of Deux-Sèvres Category:Saintonge
